Here's an example:
```latex
\documentclass{article}

\usepackage{lipsum} % This package generates random text for the example

\title{My LaTeX Document}
\author{John Doe}
\date{\today}

\begin{document}

\maketitle

\tableofcontents % This generates the table of contents

\section{Introduction}
\lipsum[1-2] % Generates random text

\section{Methods}
\lipsum[3-4] % Generates random text

\subsection{Experimental Setup}
\lipsum[5-6] % Generates random text

\subsection{Data Analysis}
